===Etymology===
From {{etyl|enm}} {{term|purpel|lang=enm}}, from {{etyl|ang}} {{term|purple|lang=ang}}, {{term|purpure||purple|lang=ang}}, from {{etyl|la}} {{term|purpura||purple dye, shellfish|lang=la}}, from {{etyl|grc}} {{term|πορφύρα||tr=porphura|purple fish|lang=grc}}, of Semitic origin.

